        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/13356438/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/13356438/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/52389870/" class=" " title="杰杰">杰杰</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="13356438">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">  写的几乎就是摇滚乐的成长史，抵制主流社会的制度的年轻人的叛逆和愤怒，颠覆主流思想的摇滚与现在的社会话题结合出越来越多的不同姿态。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-06-16 17:05</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
